sbbdep uses ELFIO for reading files in ELF binary format.
the home of ELFIO is http://elfio.sourceforge.net/ 
the ELFIO projet is maintaned by Serge Lamikhov-Center, to_serge@users.sourceforge.net


Contributions:

thanks to AlienBOB (Eric Hameleers) for his sbbdep.SlackBuild and binary distribution
http://www.slackware.com/~alien/slackbuilds/sbbdep/

thanks to Roberto Neri , rneri@libero.it
for providing excellent detailed feedback and helping with testing sbbdep


  